data.description: Outdoor living with inground pool!! Spacious 3 bedroom/ 2 bathroom with partially finished basement. explore the beautiful partially wooded 2 acre lot with creek running through back of property. Split bedroom floor plan with bonus room and den in basement. Barn-doors inclose the office and can be opened to improve flow of the living area. Attic spans entire house and can be expanded, bathroom plumbed for future expansion.
